WeS will constantly look at current and future electronic sports to make a world wide eSports community come true. Future of electronic sports: World eSports. LLC will become a major contributor to the development of electronic sports to ensure that the game developers embrace the competition side of their games and not only cater to casual gamers. WeS will be working with developers, mod developers, and anti-cheat developers on new ideas and provide strategic research through our gaming communities from our various projects.
